➜理想喊话大众，高合喊话特保戴，威马合众瞄准科创板
http://www.sohu.com/a/418227897_115873	4780
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200914/35d03ee9ba9f47d494d8335a759ace5f.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200914/1b83077ce5054165b5409632fa98d9a8.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p><strong>撰文</strong> / 朱 涵</p>
